                    <span class="u-accordion-link-text"> Discapacidad psicosocial</span><span class="u-accordion-link-icon u-accordion-link-icon-hidden u-icon u-text-grey-40 u-icon-2"><svg class="u-svg-link" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMin slice" viewBox="0 0 16 16" >
                            <use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#svg-f04f"></use>
